snippet.title: Tiny Lands - Expansion Pack 1 ( DLC)
snippet.description:
Tiny Lands DLC has arrived!
Discover more stories and relax at your own pace finding the differences in these featured worlds:

- Desert Mysteries
- City Life
- Cozy Xmas

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2211350/Tiny_Lands__Expansion_Pack_1/

This expansion pack includes 30 new handcrafted levels and stories to enjoy.
